data.description: WOW look no further. Lovely updated single-family home located in the 55+ community of Buttonwood. This home features a new roof installed in 2021, impact windows installed in 2022 and a recently installed new electric panel. Getting insurance will be worry free. Beautiful ceramic tiles throughout the entire home, designer French doors leading to the backyard, and recessed lighting throughout. This community is a hidden gem.  Hurry won't last.
